    • getUnlinkedIntegratedDemographicList

      List<MsgIntegratorDemoMap> getUnlinkedIntegratedDemographicList(LoggedInInfo loggedInInfo, int messageId)
      Retreive demographics from a remote Integrated facility that have not been linked with a local demographic. The demographic number exists only in the remote facility until the user chooses to import it. Once imported, the demographic number from the local AND remote facility will be attached.
